# KOL reference media policy (set by founder, 2026-07-19):
#   IMAGES (screenshots) → committed to GitHub, so anyone can see the references.
#   VIDEOS → NEVER committed (too large for git; kept locally for exploration only).
#
# Anything matching below is ignored in this folder + subfolders. Images
# (.png .jpg .jpeg .webp .gif .heic .svg) are NOT listed, so they are tracked.

*.mp4
*.MP4
*.mov
*.MOV
*.m4v
*.M4V
*.webm
*.WEBM
*.avi
*.AVI
*.mkv
*.MKV
*.mpg
*.mpeg
*.wmv
*.flv
